{"word":"G3456 - μυκτηρίζω - myktērízō - mook-tay-rid'-zo - Mock","slug":"G3456","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μυκτηρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>myktērízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mook-tay-rid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Mock"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03C5;&#x03BA;&#x03C4;&#x03B7;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - mukte&#x0304;rizo&#x0304;</b> - <i>mook'-tay-rid'-zo</i><p/>From a derivative of the base of <a href=\"#/G3455\">G3455</a> (meaning <i>snout</i>, as that whence <i>lowing</i> proceeds from); to <i>make mouths</i> at, that is, <i>ridicule:</i> - mock."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1592\">G1592</a>"}]}